post_survey.music_making: I am a classically trained vocalist and flutist. I have played flute since I was 8 years old. I have been singing and performing since 7 years old and studying classically since 11. I have a degree in music performance.
post_survey.habit_change: I think they have become more mature. I am looking for sound rather than lyrics. I find myself searching for music with great production or the wall of sound often achieved in classical music over lyrical meaning.
